openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Test
  description: Description
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /test/{userId}:
    get:
      operationId: getUserWithAddress
      parameters:
        - name: userId
          in: query
          description: User identity
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        default:
          description: test description
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
          links:
            Link:
              operationId: getAddress
              parameters:
                userId: $request.query.userId
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        status:
          type: integer
          description: User Status
          format: int32
          enum:
            - 1
            - 2
            - 3
      example:
        id: 123
        firstName: Ivan
        secondName: Petrov
        status: 1
